carry on , mr. bowditch this book takes place in the 1780s and is about a boy named nat bowditch . nat is great at figures and he has great perseverance . nat has just been taken out of school to help his dad make barrels for ships . but he was n't good at it at all . so his dad got him indentured for 9 years at ropes and hodges . afterwards he went on a ship and found out a new way to work lunars . after his first ship ride he went on several others and found over 2,000 mistakes in a book written by scientist . but do n't get to atached to the characters